config FIRMWARE_CUSTOMISATION
	bool "Firmware Customisation"
	label "Other"
	maintainer "SysApp"
	default y
	detail
		Operating System: RutOS (Linux based OS)
		Supported Languages: Busybox shell (ash), Lua 5.1, C, C++
		Software Development Kit (SDK): SDK archive with a build environment. Add new custom applications and libraries to an image, modify an existing component, create custom-branded firmware and web page application by changing colors, logos and other elements to fit your or your clients' needs
	detail if PYTHON_SUPPORT
		Supported Languages: \, Python
	detail if JAVA_SUPPORT
		Supported Languages: \, Java

