	imply PACKAGE_siteman
	help
		Server application for discovering, provisioning, and managing Teltonika devices over MQTT with TLS. Provides device pairing with certificate-based authentication, group management, configuration sync, and a full UBUS API.

config SITE_MANAGER_CLIENT_SUPPORT
